<br>
Damage bonus on 1h weapons doesnt scale, it will always be 11. When you start getting past 20 delay weapons, sure you can hit very high, rarely, (espcially in luclin) you will usually have a very low hit, because of the weak damage bonus, 11 at 60) Sure it has a big ass hit curve, but most of the time you will hit at the very low end of the scale. Hitting for 170 (MDS, or Dawncaller) or 1450 (Seru 1h exploit weap) isnt that great when for most of the time your hitting for a measly 12 or 14 or 30.<br>
<br>
Remember the moss covered twig? Why was it so god damn good? (at the time, before the nerf) Because its Damage bonus &gt; dly. (These other weapons being tested are closer to 2x-5xDly &gt; damagebonus. The twig had 11 damage bonus, 10 delay. Its hit curve was very small, but it still has the same damage bonus, so you'd always having &quot;Good&quot; hits very fast.<br>
<br>
Comparing Emp weap to Crappy dragon 1h pal weapon is both fair and unfair. Unfair because of the ease of getting one, fair because they are still The Best, or damn near the best (in terms of ratio)<br>
