I couldn't disagree more, Warriors need MORE dps not less AND the ability to hold agro.  See below...<br>
<br>
My perspective: level 60 raid oriented warrior, my guild has cleared Vex Thal, etc, etc.<br>
<br>
Assumption on the shield change: I am assuming that 1h weapon + shield will become comprable to dual wield damage but a bit less.  It certainly won't exceed dual wield damage or there's no reason to dual wield.  So for this discussion i'll just say let's assume Verant makes the two equal via new 1h weapons, shields, etc.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Raiding:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
On raids only warriors who end up tanking are actually needed.  If you have no slip-ups and no warriors die you only need 1 for most raids, so lets add 2 more in for mistakes and say 3 warriors is plenty sufficient.  Any warriors after those 3 are a detriment to the raid...we do less damage than any other melee class and we have *zero* utlity.  Replace us with literally *any* other class and we improve the raid.  <br>
<br>
The shield change above will improve the warriors that tank, hey we'll tank better great!  However, every other warrior on the raid will be unchanged.  To use the new 1h &amp; shield won't increase our damage so we'll stay the same and gosh that makes us the worst class in all of eq for the raid.  We need more damage or utility to fix this.  <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Grouping:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Healers in my guild have enough FT and Monks in my guild tank well enough that the healer (dru/shm/clr it doesn't matter) has plenty of mana left over for nuking.  So in an exp group if a monk tanks just fine and dandy why would you ever want a warrior in group?  To lower the groups damage output?  I can't see any situation when I'd want the above shield/1h combo to lower my damage and raise my ability to tank when monks/pallys/sk's tank fine enough for groups to be better with them than with me...oh and they all get/hold agro better than warriors as well.  Again the solution here is we need more dps or more utility.<br>
<br>
So Absor its fine for you to say that this isn't all the changes but really this does *nothing* for the class.  <br>
<br>
1. Fix our agro with every weapon setup (2h, dual 1h, 1h/shield)<br>
2. Increase our dps...why do rogues double my damage on raids?  Why do monks do almost double my damage?  <br>
3. Give us some utility...if we aren't wanted for our damage and our ability to tank isnt needed as monks and knights tank just fine then we need something to do on raids/groups.<br>
